## P5 Wiki Semantic Search - Implementation Plan
**Status:** draft
**Tags:** stack:both, module:wiki, priority:P3
**Depends on:** G18, G31, D25

### Overview
Implement semantic vector search for wiki pages using FAISS to improve retrieval accuracy and enable RAG-based knowledge discovery.

### Phase Breakdown

| Phase | Task | Owner | Duration | Dependencies | Status | Detail |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| P5.1 | Integrate embedding computation | Coder | 1 day | D25 | draft | Add embedding computation using local model or API-based embeddings. Create embedding service that accepts text and returns 384-dim vectors. Implement batch embedding for wiki pages. Deliverable: Embedding service returns vectors, batch processing works. |
| P5.2 | Create vector storage layer | Coder | 1 day | P5.1 | draft | Implement vector storage for wiki page embeddings using FAISS. Store 384-dim vectors with page metadata. Add vector index persistence to {project}/wiki/.index/faiss. Deliverable: Vector index stores and retrieves embeddings. |
| P5.3 | Enhance query_wiki tool | Coder | 1 day | P5.2, D25 | draft | Update query_wiki tool to use FAISS vector similarity search (top-K retrieval). Combine full-text search with semantic search for hybrid results. Add relevance ranking with similarity scores and excerpts. Deliverable: query_wiki returns semantic results, hybrid search works. |
| P5.4 | Update frontend search UI | Coder | 0.5 day | P5.3 | draft | Modify WikiView search to show semantic results with excerpts and scores. Display relevance ranking indicators. Add toggle between text-only and hybrid search modes. Deliverable: Search UI shows semantic results with scores. |
| P5.5 | Performance optimization | Coder | 0.5 day | P5.2, P5.3 | draft | Optimize vector search to return results in <500ms for 1000 pages. Implement caching for frequent queries. Add pagination for large result sets. Deliverable: Vector search latency <500ms for 1000 pages. |

### Success Criteria
- Embedding computation works for all wiki pages
- Vector storage persists and retrieves embeddings correctly
- query_wiki returns top-K semantic results with relevance scores
- Hybrid search (text + semantic) improves retrieval accuracy
- Vector search performance <500ms for 1000-page wiki

