## P6 AutoDown Editor - Implementation Plan
**Status:** draft
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:editor, priority:P3
**Depends on:** G19, G32, A11, D27

### Overview
Implement Tiptap-based WYSIWYG editor for Wiki and Spec content with Markdown/AutoDown serialization and custom block extensions.

### Phase Breakdown

| Phase | Task | Owner | Duration | Dependencies | Status | Detail |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| P6.1 | Integrate Tiptap editor core | Coder | 1 day | D27 | draft | Install Tiptap dependencies (@tiptap/vue-3, @tiptap/starter-kit, @tiptap/markdown). Create AutoDownEditor.vue with Vue 3 composition API. Initialize Editor instance with StarterKit blocks. Deliverable: Editor renders, basic blocks work (paragraph, heading, list). |
| P6.2 | Implement slash command palette | Coder | 0.5 day | P6.1 | draft | Add SlashCommand extension with configurable menu items. Implement keyboard handling for "/" trigger, arrow key navigation, Enter selection, Escape dismissal. Filter items by search query. Deliverable: Slash menu opens on "/", filters correctly, inserts blocks. |
| P6.3 | Implement bubble menu | Coder | 0.5 day | P6.1 | draft | Add BubbleMenu extension for inline formatting (bold, italic, code, link). Show menu on text selection, hide on blur. Implement formatting commands (toggle bold/italic/etc.). Deliverable: Bubble menu appears on selection, formats text. |
| P6.4 | Implement drag handle | Coder | 0.5 day | P6.1 | draft | Add DragHandle extension for block reordering. Show handle on block hover, enable drag-and-drop reordering. Update document order on drop. Deliverable: Drag handle appears, blocks reorder on drag. |
| P6.5 | Implement Markdown round-trip | Coder | 0.5 day | P6.1 | draft | Configure @tiptap/markdown extension for bidirectional sync. Implement load from string (parse) and save to string (serialize). Verify no data loss in round-trip. Deliverable: Markdown loads and saves correctly, no corruption. |
| P6.6 | Replace MarkdownEditor in views | Coder | 0.5 day | P6.5 | draft | Update WikiView to use AutoDownEditor instead of MarkdownEditor for edit/create modes. Update SpecView category editors to use AutoDownEditor. Deliverable: Wiki and Spec views use new editor. |
| P6.7 | Add AutoDown extensions (Phase 2) | Coder | 2 day | P6.6 | draft | Implement Callout block with info/warning/tip/danger types. Add Math block with KaTeX rendering. Implement Mermaid diagram block with live rendering. Add Spec reference block [[G1]] with clickable links. Deliverable: Custom blocks render correctly, serialize to markdown. |

### Success Criteria
- Tiptap editor core integrated with Vue 3
- Slash command palette inserts all StarterKit blocks
- Bubble menu applies inline formatting
- Drag handle reorders blocks
- Markdown round-trip works without data loss
- AutoDown custom blocks render and serialize correctly

